==Port of a CSGO Map made by Hypilix==
This port was made a while ago, just uploading for the sake of preserving map ports

Original CSGO Version: https://gamebanana.com/mods/79413

Watch the video : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1miA2i6Mtow

==Many games==

- Climb extreme
- Football and Volleyball
- Boo's Attack (Boo and Goomba)
- Rainbow Spleef
- Rainbow Climb (x3, one by round) - Will be re-added in an upcoming update :)
- Rainbow Bhop
- Rainbow Race
- Mario kart, race with booster and obstacle
- Deathrace with Bowser, etc
- Deathrun
- Moving Floor
- Coin game (new games)
- Hunger games (battle balloon map Mario Kart Wii)

Many secrets and vents - check the video

Map for the Gamebanana mapping contest 2018 :
3rd Place Winner!!!

Link : https://gamebanana.com/contests/93
